#: ../../../source/docs/api_reference/val.h.rst:16
msgid ""
"This class is a C++ data type that can be used to represent (and provide "
"convenient access to) any JavaScript object. You can use it to call a "
"JavaScript object, read and write its properties, or coerce it to a C++ "
"value like a ``bool``, ``int``, or ``std::string``."
msgstr ""

